          <h2 id="section1">Introduction</h2>
          <p>The elevator industry in India is experiencing robust growth, driven by high-rise residential and commercial developments across metros and emerging cities. As vertical mobility becomes indispensable, the importance of selecting a dependable elevator partner grows. 
          The right partner influences not only the initial installation quality but also ongoing maintenance, technology upgrades, and safety compliance, all of which impact project success and occupant experience.</p>
